			<link linkend="Portlet Lifecycle">Portlet Lifecycle</link>
			: GateIn portlets are built with WebUI
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			<link linkend="Portal Lifecycle">Portal Lifecycle</link>
			: GateIn portal himself is a WebUI application
		</listitem>
		<listitem>
			How-to
			<link linkend="Create a WebUI Portlet">Create a WebUI Portlet</link>
			: Learn how to write your own app with WebUI
		</listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
</section>